崗位。</span></span></strong>對於本港出現首宗確診患者死亡個案，羅卓堯說出現社區感染個案，是由於政府無法堵截源頭，若出現大型爆發，他形容是政府漠視社會訴求所致。"},{"pid":"65b079565234b1d24744947a75b47709c4f35f74","tid":1861680,"uid":293,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"呼籲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62410f4997e0e46e06c6d8633b72704e2172fead","tid":1861680,"uid":15391,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"等睇打手話我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公會現形記"},{"pid":"7ca5927a54049b9e5611ef98cb4cda112179fa7e","tid":1861680,"uid":53524,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"社區爆發果陣封關都無用，明唔明？"},{"pid":"7b8817d073ffd844147a64a6f90ede3a46130e34","tid":1861680,"uid":126283,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"社區大爆發係政府問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同醫護完全無關"},{"pid":"bb3782a27f571ecffa0f6a8d6db7df7f1c22ae46","tid":1861680,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"咁其實咪姐係叫大家返去比人清算"},{"pid":"816221a02aceca8a702b362a6f3779f3a2860223","tid":1861680,"uid":15391,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"大爆發就係政府既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護執包伏走啦，仲要返去用條命幫佢執屎？<br />\n工會傻架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536da28cb704d514f0509e0255c1999ddd49dff1","tid":1861680,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d3e59dda3590868162bca7e1b91a3d25e8211f2","tid":1861680,"uid":78392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:44:40.00